import React from 'react'
import { Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

import SignIn from '../pages/Signin'
import RouteHandler from '../components/RouteHandler'


const Routes = () => {
    return (
        <Switch>
            <RouteHandler exact path='/'>
                <SignIn />
            </RouteHandler>
        </Switch>
    )

}

export default Routes
